Look at this beauty 😍🦚 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on earthfever.net (link in my bio: @earthfever)

Peacock in a courtship display!

The ornate train is believed to be the result of sexual selection by the females. Males use their ornate trains in a courtship display: they raise the feathers into a fan and quiver them.

📽 @l.fernandes24
